          Validate Against JSON Schema
        </span>
        <svg id="schema-chevron" class="w-4 h-4 text-mute transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
      </button>
